    <id>https://anxgang.github.io/post/series/S02_rails/C01_rails_starter/series-rails-starter-02.html</id>
    <published>2020-03-24T22:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-24T22:50:08.874Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安裝套件管理工具"><a href="#安裝套件管理工具" class="headerlink" title="安裝套件管理工具"></a>安裝套件管理工具</h2><p>請務必安裝 homebrew</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/bin/bash -c <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)</span>"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安裝終端機"><a href="#安裝終端機" class="headerlink" title="安裝終端機"></a>安裝終端機</h2><p>建議安裝 iTerm2 取代原有的 Terminal</p><h4 id="安裝-iterm2"><a href="#安裝-iterm2" class="headerlink" title="安裝 iterm2"></a>安裝 iterm2</h4><p>請直接到 <a href="https://www.iterm2.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.iterm2.com/</a> 下載安裝</p><h4 id="安裝-zsh"><a href="#安裝-zsh" class="headerlink" title="安裝 zsh"></a>安裝 zsh</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安裝-oh-my-zsh-套件"><a href="#安裝-oh-my-zsh-套件" class="headerlink" title="安裝 oh-my-zsh 套件"></a>安裝 oh-my-zsh 套件</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh -c <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh)</span>"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安裝編輯器"><a href="#安裝編輯器" class="headerlink" title="安裝編輯器"></a>安裝編輯器</h2><p>建議可以安裝 VSCode 當作主要的編輯器<br><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://code.visualstudio.com/</a></p><h2 id="安裝-Rails-和-RVM-版本管理"><a href="#安裝-Rails-和-RVM-版本管理" class="headerlink" title="安裝 Rails 和 RVM 版本管理"></a>安裝 Rails 和 RVM 版本管理</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gpg2 --recv-keys 409B6B1796C275462A1703113804BB82D39DC0E3 7D2BAF1CF37B13E2069D6956105BD0E739499BDB</span><br><span class="line">\curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable --rails</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="設定-git"><a href="#設定-git" class="headerlink" title="設定 git"></a>設定 git</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;YOUR NAME&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;YOUR@EMAIL.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安裝資料庫"><a href="#安裝資料庫" class="headerlink" title="安裝資料庫"></a>安裝資料庫</h2><h4 id="6-1-安裝-sqlite3"><a href="#6-1-安裝-sqlite3" class="headerlink" title="6.1 安裝 sqlite3"></a>6.1 安裝 sqlite3</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install sqlite3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="6-2-安裝-postgresql"><a href="#6-2-安裝-postgresql" class="headerlink" title="6.2 安裝 postgresql"></a>6.2 安裝 postgresql</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install postgresql</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 設定開機啟用服務</span></span><br><span class="line">brew services start postgresql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>參考</p><ol><li><a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-configure-your-macos-terminal-with-zsh-like-a-pro-c0ab3f3c1156/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-configure-your-macos-terminal-with-zsh-like-a-pro-c0ab3f3c1156/</a></li><li><a href="https://gorails.com/setup/osx/10.15-catalina" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://gorails.com/setup/osx/10.15-catalina</a></li></ol></blockquote>]]></content>
    
